<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Products - ElectroStore</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header', { user: user, cart: cart }) %>

    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            <% if (typeof message !== 'undefined' && message) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-info">
                    <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> <%= message %>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            
            <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-error">
                    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> <%= error %>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
                <h1><i class="fas fa-store"></i> Electronics Store</h1>
                <div>
                    <a href="/cart" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i> View Cart
                        <% if (cart && cart.length > 0) { %>
                            <span class="cart-count"><%= cart.length %></span>
                        <% } %>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">
                        <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Welcome to ElectroStore
                    </h3>
                    <p>Browse our selection of premium electronics. Add items to your cart and checkout to practice Blind XSS injection in the delivery notes field.</p>
                    
                    <div class="security-warning">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        <strong>Security Training:</strong> This lab demonstrates a real XSS vulnerability. Inject payloads in delivery notes during checkout.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="products-grid">
                <% products.forEach(product => { %>
                    <div class="product-card">
                        <div class="product-image">
                            <i class="fas fa-laptop"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="product-content">
                            <h3 class="product-title"><%= product.name %></h3>
                            <p class="product-description"><%= product.description %></p>
                            
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                                <div class="product-price">$<%= product.price.toFixed(2) %></div>
                                <div class="product-stock <%= product.stock > 5 ? 'in-stock' : product.stock > 0 ? 'low-stock' : 'out-of-stock' %>">
                                    <i class="fas fa-box"></i>
                                    <%= product.stock > 0 ? product.stock + ' in stock' : 'Out of stock' %>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <form action="/cart/add" method="POST" class="d-flex gap-2">
                                <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= product.id %>">
                                <div class="form-group" style="flex: 1;">
                                    <input 
                                        type="number" 
                                        name="quantity" 
                                        class="form-control" 
                                        value="1" 
                                        min="1" 
                                        max="<%= product.stock %>"
                                        <%= product.stock === 0 ? 'disabled' : '' %>
                                    >
                                </div>
                                <button 
                                    type="submit" 
                                    class="btn btn-primary"
                                    <%= product.stock === 0 ? 'disabled' : '' %>
                                >
                                    <i class="fas fa-cart-plus"></i> Add to Cart
                                </button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            </div>

            <div class="card mt-4">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h3 class="card-title">
                        <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> How to Practice XSS
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="row" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
                        <div>
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i> Step 1: Add to Cart</h4>
                            <p>Select products and add them to your shopping cart.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i> Step 2: Checkout</h4>
                            <p>Proceed to checkout and fill in shipping details.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-bug"></i> Step 3: Inject Payload</h4>
                            <p>Enter XSS payload in "Delivery Notes" field:</p>
                            <code><!-- <script>alert('XSS')</script> --></code>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-robot"></i> Step 4: Wait for Bot</h4>
                            <p>Admin bot views new orders every 60 seconds, triggering your payload.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="xss-warning mt-3">
                        <h4>
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> XSS Vulnerability Details
                        </h4>
                        <p>The admin order details page uses unescaped output (<code><%- %></code>) instead of escaped output (<code><%= %></code>) for delivery notes, allowing script execution.</p>
                        <p><strong>Real-world impact:</strong> Steal admin session cookies, redirect to malicious sites, or perform actions as admin.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
